parameters: \TA[1]No, even if you say that, it's troublesome.
\TA[1]I'm eating with this, you know. It's consensual, right?

\TA[1]I don't remember giving you permission to touch me!? Don't
make up things on your own!

\TA[1]This is not a joke. If you don't delete it, I will sue
you.

\TA[1]If you want, I can even take the video and go to the
police.

\TA[1]Well, I don't know if the important people will do anything
for an unidentified girl who isn't even a citizen, lol.

\TA[1](Indeed. As a magical girl, I can't file a lawsuit or report
it.)(If I do something like that, the fact that I am
Levantia will become widely known.)

\TA[1]Could it be that they had planned everything up to this
point...?
\TA[1]It seems like they noticed from looking at my expression.

\TA[1]You were enjoying it too, weren't you? If you didn't like
it, you should have resisted.

\TA[1]At that time, I was drunk and I stayed still because I was
afraid I might cause a serious injury!

\TA[1]Oh, really? I see, you're truly a heroine of justice. But I
wonder if others think the same?
\TA[1]Alright. Finally, we can understand each other.
